---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="关于我 | SY-Jia06"
    description="关于 SY-Jia06，吉林大学唐敖庆班学生。"
    active="about"
    canonical="/about/"
    type="profile"
    includeLightbox={true}
>
    <main>
        <div class="subpage-shell">
            <div class="about-profile-card">
                <div class="about-cover"></div>
                <div class="about-profile-layout">
                    <aside class="about-sidebar">
                        <div class="about-avatar-ring">
                            <button class="post-image-trigger" data-lightbox-src="/assets/avatar.jpg" data-lightbox-alt="SY-Jia06" style="all: unset; display: block; width: 100%; height: 100%; cursor: zoom-in; border-radius: 50%;">
                                <img src="/assets/avatar.jpg" alt="SY-Jia06" class="about-avatar-img" />
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <h1 class="about-name">SY-Jia06</h1>
                        <p class="about-handle">audio curious · backend learner</p>
                        <div class="about-contact-list">
                            <a class="about-contact-item" href="https://github.com/SY-Jia06" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
                                <span class="contact-icon" aria-hidden="true">GH</span>
                                <span class="contact-text">GitHub / SY-Jia06</span>
                            </a>
                            <a class="about-contact-item" href="mailto:a168995738@outlook.com">
                                <span class="contact-icon" aria-hidden="true">@</span>
                                <span class="contact-text">Outlook / a168995738@outlook.com</span>
                            </a>
                            <span class="about-contact-item">
                                <span class="contact-icon" aria-hidden="true">CN</span>
                                <span class="contact-text">Location / Changchun, China</span>
                            </span>
                            <span class="about-contact-item">
                                <span class="contact-icon" aria-hidden="true">AI</span>
                                <span class="contact-text">Focus / Audio, Backend</span>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </aside>

                    <section class="about-main">
                        <blockquote class="about-quote">Hi, 我是 J.</blockquote>
                        <div class="about-copy">
                            <p>吉林大学大二 CS 在读。</p>
                            <p>我喜欢向内探索，关于人，关于存在；也喜欢向外挖掘，关于技术，关于那些还没被解决的问题。</p>
                            <p>Current focus：🎧 Audio + 🛠️ Backend。跟进 AI 前沿，日常在 Codex 和 Notion 里度过。</p>
                            <p>我是存在主义者，<em>existence is something I build deliberately</em>。也带着人本主义跟人打交道。</p>
                            <p>我不 follow 「principals」，我做自己真正在意的事。</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="about-section-block">
                            <h2>All the way here</h2>
                            <div class="git-tree">
                                <div class="g-node">
                                    <div class="g-line"></div>
                                    <div class="g-dot"></div>
                                    <div class="g-content">
                                        <div class="g-time">大一上 - 大一下</div>
                                        <h3 class="g-title">算法竞赛</h3>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="g-node">
                                    <div class="g-line"></div>
                                    <div class="g-dot"></div>
                                    <div class="g-content">
                                        <div class="g-time">大一下暑假 - 大二上</div>
                                        <h3 class="g-title">进入 AI4S 课题组</h3>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="g-node">
                                    <div class="g-line"></div>
                                    <div class="g-dot"></div>
                                    <div class="g-content">
                                        <div class="g-time">2026.02 - Present</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="g-branch">
                                    <div class="g-branch-line"></div>
                                    <div class="g-node" style="padding-bottom: 24px;">
                                        <div class="g-line"></div>
                                        <div class="g-dot" style="border-color: #0ea5e9;"></div>
                                        <div class="g-content">
                                            <div class="g-time">MCM-A<br />Done</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="g-branch">
                                    <div class="g-branch-line"></div>
                                    <div class="g-node" style="padding-bottom: 24px;">
                                        <div class="g-line"></div>
                                        <div class="g-dot" style="border-color: #0ea5e9;"></div>
                                        <div class="g-content">
                                            <div class="g-time">大创<br />Ongoing</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="g-branch">
                                    <div class="g-branch-line"></div>
                                    <div class="g-node" style="padding-bottom: 0;">
                                        <div class="g-line g-line-last"></div>
                                        <div class="g-dot" style="border-color: #0ea5e9;"></div>
                                        <div class="g-content">
                                            <div class="g-time">Audio<br />Ongoing</div>
                                            <p style="margin: 8px 0 0; color: var(--text-body); font-size: 0.95rem;">Papers I'm reading: <a href="https://daffy-milk-c9c.notion.site/fdb1e500221941f99a7aefba88d5c417?v=8921a98f2ae34bb6bdcfc2dfcbc5d329&source=copy_link" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" style="color: var(--accent);">🔗 Notion</a></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="g-branch">
                                    <div class="g-branch-line"></div>
                                    <div class="g-node" style="padding-bottom: 0;">
                                        <div class="g-line g-line-last"></div>
                                        <div class="g-dot" style="border-color: #0ea5e9;"></div>
                                        <div class="g-content">
                                            <div class="g-time">服创RL<br />Ongoing</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>
